  "title": "Python for Everybody: Exploring Data Using Python 3",
  "description": "This book is designed to introduce students to programming =
and computational thinking through the lens of exploring data. You can think =
of Python as your tool to solve data problems that are beyond the capability =
of a spreadsheet. Python is an easy to use and easy to learn programming lang=
uage that is freely available on Macintosh, Windows, or Linux computers. Ther=
